Story by [](https://apnews.com/)
TALES AZZONI
Thu, January 29, 2026 at 3:06 PM UTC Â·

MADRID (AP) â€” A day after a stunning last-minute loss to Benfica in the Champions League, Real Madrid returns its focus to La Liga knowing that it needs to improve.
Coaches and players were on the same page after the 4-2 defeat in Lisbon left the club in the first knockout stage of the Champions League, taking responsibility for a poor performance and a lack of attitude.

â€œThe games start on minute zero and not on minute 45, so in the end the defeat is deserved," said Kylian MbappÃ©, who scored both Madrid goals on Wednesday to take his Champions League-leading tally to 13. "I canâ€™t say itâ€™s not deserved because we didnâ€™t play well to win this game. They did. Benfica at home is always difficult. It was our fault.â€
Section Title: Real Madrid refocuses on La Liga after stunning loss to Benfica
Content:
MbappÃ© said it seemed the team didn't take the game as seriously as it should have. Goalkeeper Anatoliy Trubin scored Benfica's fourth goal in [the last minute](https://apnews.com/article/trubin-benfica-real-madrid-champions-league-33b7eef1a0675a2d02bb1c704098a017) , securing the Portuguese side the goal difference it needed to make it to the top 24. Madrid needed only a draw but defeat cost it a top eight automatic position in the round of 16.
â€œBenfica were playing for their lives and we didnâ€™t look like we were playing for ours," MbappÃ© said. "That was the big problem of the game. At the start, both teams had things to play for, we were in the top eight and they were in the top 24. We saw how Benfica played but we didnâ€™t see what was at stake.â€
Madrid coach Ãlvaro Arbeloa said he wasn't able to convey to his players the importance of the game to Benfica.

Real Madrid hosts city rival Rayo Vallecano on Sunday. Madrid has won five in a row in La Liga to cut its deficit to leader Barcelona to only one point. Rayo has lost three consecutive games across all tournaments and sits 16th in the standings, near the relegation zone.
